structure.unit: SALES OF REALTY OF PERSONS UNDER DISABILITY (Superseded)

law.history: Repealed 1982 Ky. Acts ch. 277, sec. 21, effective July 15, 1982. -- Amended 1980 Ky. Acts ch. 160, sec. 1, effective July 15, 1980. -- Amended 1978 Ky. Acts ch. 384, sec. 512, effective June 17, 1978. -- Amended 1974 Ky. Acts ch. 386, sec. 74. -- Transferred 1952 Ky. Acts ch. 84, sec. 1, effective July 1, 1953, from C.C. sec. 494.

metadata.note: . 1980 Ky. Acts ch. 396, sec. 114 would have amended this section effective July 1, 1982. However, 1980 Ky. Acts ch. 396 was repealed by 1982 Ky. Acts ch. 141, sec. 146, also effective July 1, 1982.
